as an international student.

00:22:38.640 --> 00:22:40.260
And then moved out there.

00:22:40.260 --> 00:22:41.760
So, basically,
when I come here--

00:22:41.760 --> 00:22:43.854
and I didn't tell
my family why I'm

00:22:43.854 --> 00:22:45.520
