00:23:10.110 --> 00:23:17.010
And after that, things went
a little bit difficult for me

00:23:17.010 --> 00:23:19.020
when I was in San Francisco.

00:23:19.020 --> 00:23:23.150
And then I moved in New
York City two months after.

00:23:23.150 --> 00:23:29.280
Then one month after that, I
heard about LGBT community.

00:23:29.280 --> 00:23:32.200
Because in Africa, we
don't have LGBT community.

00:23:32.200 --> 00:23:36.720
The thing is, I didn't
really know why we have

00:23:36.720 --> 00:23:39.210
LGBT community here in Africa--

