00:58:35.910 --> 00:58:38.020
LGBT community is
a LGBT community.

00:58:38.020 --> 00:58:40.850
Like, African LGBT community,
American LGBT community,

00:58:40.850 --> 00:58:41.900
doesn't matter, you know?

00:58:41.900 --> 00:58:43.130
We all LGBT community.

00:58:43.130 --> 00:58:47.466
And I think we have to think
about them, too, you know?

00:58:47.466 --> 00:58:48.050
Yeah.

00:58:48.050 --> 00:58:49.532
That's everything I have to say.

00:58:49.532 --> 00:58:51.740
