people, as Soul was describing,

00:59:12.770 --> 00:59:14.240
it's a whole other thing, right?

00:59:14.240 --> 00:59:16.580
So speaking up about
that, that the stakes

00:59:16.580 --> 00:59:18.320
are so high for
some of these people

00:59:18.320 --> 00:59:21.080
going back to countries where
