01:02:57.760 --> 01:03:11.870
literally the only, that we know
of, the only openly homosexual.

01:03:11.870 --> 01:03:13.505
I'm the only--

01:03:13.505 --> 01:03:17.960
I'm the LGBT and
the Q of the family.

01:03:17.960 --> 01:03:19.340
Just that one.

01:03:22.870 --> 01:03:34.910
But while I was growing up, I
never really actually came out.

01:03:39.650 --> 01:03:40.790
It just happened.

01:03:40.790 --> 01:03:44.640
And they found out, so I--

01:03:44.640 --> 01:03:47.435
I guess my mom and
my sister had just--

01:03:47.435 --> 01:03:49.610
well, my sister, she
then knew, I guess.

01:03:49.610 --> 01:03:51.860
She just knew this whole time.

01:03:51.860 --> 01:03:54.802
Didn't inform me that she knew.

01:03:54.802 --> 01:04:00.470
