01:04:11.280 --> 01:04:14.225
It took them a while to
really be OK with it.

01:04:14.225 --> 01:04:17.840
But then they were like, oh, OK.

01:04:17.840 --> 01:04:19.225
All right.

01:04:19.225 --> 01:04:19.725
Sure.

01:04:22.340 --> 01:04:28.840
