01:04:58.190 --> 01:05:01.790
Because I'm pretty sure
sometimes they want to tell you

01:05:01.790 --> 01:05:04.390
but they're not sure
how you would take it.

01:05:04.390 --> 01:05:07.670
Have an open mind.

01:05:07.670 --> 01:05:09.630
A clear mindset.

01:05:09.630 --> 01:05:12.080
And enter it without hostility.

01:05:12.080 --> 01:05:17.430
Just go in with--

01:05:17.430 --> 01:05:21.640
just go into the
conversation without--

01:05:27.130 --> 01:05:28.090
what's the word for it?

01:05:28.090 --> 01:05:30.340
I guess without violence.

01:05:33.137 --> 01:05:34.720
And don't try to
force it out of them.

01:05:34.720 --> 01:05:36.560
Don't try to force
it out of them.

01:05:36.560 --> 01:05:39.060
Because if they're already--
