01:05:39.060 --> 01:05:42.380
a hard time telling you, just--

01:05:42.380 --> 01:05:45.270
when they feel it's time
for them to tell you,

01:05:45.270 --> 01:05:48.070
just let them tell you.

01:05:48.070 --> 01:05:53.449
Don't be harsh about it.

01:05:53.449 --> 01:05:55.240
Of course, you know,
if they don't like it,

01:05:55.240 --> 01:05:56.130
they won't like it.

01:05:56.130 --> 01:05:59.170
But still be supporting--

01:06:01.910 --> 01:06:04.980
just be there for them in
any way, shape or form.

01:06:04.980 --> 01:06:06.960
Because it will make--

01:06:06.960 --> 01:06:13.050
trust me, it will make that
young boy or young girl,

01:06:13.050 --> 01:06:17.184
whichever one, it will make
them feel a whole lot better.

