01:06:56.340 --> 01:06:59.471
Giving a message that
these people are other.

01:06:59.471 --> 01:06:59.970
Right?

01:06:59.970 --> 01:07:02.220
And that absolutely
contributes to violence

01:07:02.220 --> 01:07:03.580
