01:07:25.740 --> 01:07:27.510
But it's actually all the same.

01:07:27.510 --> 01:07:30.179
So as we go forward and
advocating and fighting

01:07:30.179 --> 01:07:32.220
against this, I think it's
important to keep that

01:07:32.220 --> 01:07:34.350
at the front of our minds.

